<section class="section section--tint is5-steps">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="is5-steps__heading">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>

    <div class="is5-steps__grid">

      <div class="is5-steps__step">
        <h3 class="is5-steps__step-title">Personalized Consultation</h3>
        <p class="is5-steps__step-body">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="is5-steps__step">
        <h3 class="is5-steps__step-title">Relax and Recharge</h3>
        <p class="is5-steps__step-body">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="is5-steps__step">
        <h3 class="is5-steps__step-title">Feel the Benefits</h3>
        <p class="is5-steps__step-body">Many patients report feeling more energized and refreshed immediately after their session. The full benefits will support your system for days to come, helping you maintain that feeling of peak wellness.&#8203;</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .is5-steps__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .is5-steps__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .is5-steps__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .is5-steps__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .is5-steps__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .is5-steps__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
